videos.description: Arkansas State DE Caleb Caston picks up the Andre Nunez fumble and returns it 24 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Red Wolves' defense returns fumble for TD

videos.description: Johnston White dives over the top of the defense for the 1-yard touchdown run to extend the Arkansas State lead.

videos.description: Louisiana's Jarvis Jeffries recovers a fumbled hand off in the first quarter.

videos.description: Arkansas State's Michael Johnson intercepts Andre Nunez in the end zone for the games 3rd turnover.
videos.headline: Red Wolves' defense forces second turnover

videos.headline: McInnis takes it 44 yards for Red Wolves TD

videos.description: Red Wolves QB Justice Hanson takes the keeper 20 yards for the score as Arkansas State begins to pull away in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Hanson keeps it himself for TD

videos.headline: Red Wolves pull fake spike for TD
